  "decision": "CLI `_validate_endpoint(url)` should delegate to a narrow `is_loopback_only(url)` wrapper — NOT to `classify_url` which permits ALL non-public (loopback OR 10.x OR 192.168.x OR link-local). Private-LAN endpoints are disallowed too: host machine in phase-7 architecture is reached via SSH reverse tunnel on 127.0.0.1:<port>, so rejecting non-loopback is strictly correct."
